summary:
- Art Director and beauty hunter with a special focus on the issue of inclusiveness.
- I am a multifaceted, versatile and creative person, with a Master degree in Arts Management (IED Roma-Firenze-Venezia) and a bachelor degree in Art Direction and Graphic Design, achieved at Naba Milano. 
-I have had experiences in the world of contemporary art as Executive Assistant and Social media manager at Von Buren Contemporary in Rome. 
-I am currently following a personal digital project (@Neodecadentismo) which is dedicated to unmasking the link between ancient and contemporary in the art field, and I primarily address generation z. One of my main objectives remains to bring young audiences closer to the world of art and culture and the institutions that are part of it (including museums and galleries).
- In my free time I love reading, walking, listening to classical music and I am very passionate about the world of gaming. Obviously as a great lover of art you will find me very often at exhibitions and museums:)
